data.description:
Come check out and fall in love with this gorgeous 6-bedroom, 2-bath home. This gem sits on an expansive corner lot, which features a nice front porch, low-maintenance vinyl siding, separate garage , a large fenced-in back yard (with patio furniture & pop-up gazebo which are included in the sale). Immaculate and plenty of bells and whistles. You are welcomed by a spacious living room that boasts new vinyl plank flooring (found throughout), a large picture window, and a ceiling fan. Galley style kitchen with ample counter space, plenty of floor to ceiling cabinets, and gorgeous subway tile backsplash that runs the length of the kitchen. Through the kitchen, you will find a spacious living room that is perfect for entertaining. The main floor also features 2 bedrooms and a full bath. The second floor includes an additional four bedrooms and a full bath making this your perfect next home for a big family.
Refrigerator, washer and dryer are not included in the sale. Home being sold As-Is.
